# E-ink PDF Templates

A production-ready system to create interactive PDF templates optimized for Boox Onyx e-readers, featuring internal navigation, bookmarks, and form fields. Designed with device-specific profiles, dual export modes (interactive/flattened), and ground-truth preview fidelity for reliable e-ink performance.

## Features

- **Device Profiles**: Optimized for different Boox models (Note Air 4C, Tab Ultra C, etc.)
- **Dual Export Modes**: Interactive AcroForms or flattened graphics
- **Ground Truth Preview**: Server-side PNG preview that exactly matches PDF output
- **E-ink Optimization**: Automatic constraint enforcement (fonts, strokes, touch targets)
- **Deterministic Builds**: Reproducible PDFs for testing and validation
- **Template Library**: Professional templates for productivity, education, and reading

## Installation

```bash
pip install einkpdf
```

## Quick Start

```bash
# Generate a PDF template
einkpdf render daily-planner.yaml output.pdf --profile Boox-Note-Air-4C

# Validate template
einkpdf validate template.yaml --strict

# Generate preview
einkpdf preview template.yaml --page 1 --output preview.png
```

